================================================================================
SAMPLE LOG — Error Handling Scenarios
================================================================================
This log demonstrates the bot's error handling for various failure modes:
validation errors, API errors, network failures, and retry with backoff.
================================================================================

--- Validation Error: Missing price for LIMIT order ---

